Private Hendersson's last log entry
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dear Lord, they all went mad!
From the beginning, they've shown an unhealthy interest in the monolith. Scientists, marines, even the staff. 
Within a month, we got three cases of suicide. Two white coats and private Fitch. Then, a janitor has lost his mind.


We should've packed and left this place. Instead, the expedition lead cut off connection to the HQ and ordered an investigation. 
Two other scientists shot themselves and private Rodrigez stopped recognizing others. When captain gave order to hand all weapons to him, a revolt broke out.
Most died in the shooting. I've locked myself in a lab room, together with a white coat. 
She whispered about some discovery before she stopped talking.


I'm alone now. Half of the people is dead, the other half is staring at walls. I will go to the monolith. I want to know...